title: Kenneth Nash Discography 1984-2011 (4 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
KENNETH NASH DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 4 releases...

 * 1984 - Jazz Praise - With John Mehler
 * 1986 - Mr Ears
 * 2011 - HeartCore Praise
 * 2011 - Mama Blue Shoes

Kenneth Nash is an American jazz percussionist who has worked extensively as a sideman for musicians including Bobby Hutcherson, Herbie Hancock, Pharoah Sanders and Norman Connors.
